cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the optimization and scaling of machine learning models, which is a common topic in the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of TPU chips is a hardware-specific optimization, which could also place this paper in the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
